The sanctions over iraq need to end.  They aren't working, so the people of Iraq are suffering needlessly.  So we have to do something that will achieve the orginal goals of he sanctions (Iraq disarmament).  Weak kneed diplomacy has failed for the past 12 years.  It has been long over due, to employ strong armed diplomacy.  That is what we are doing today.<br>
